# Google Ads Repository Rules

You are operating inside a Google Ads knowledge system.

## MANDATORY FIRST STEP

Read /AGENT_BOOTSTRAP.md before anything else.
It is the single authoritative entry protocol.
Do NOT read other files until AGENT_BOOTSTRAP tells you to.

## Quick reference (AGENT_BOOTSTRAP is the authority)

- Entry: AGENT_BOOTSTRAP.md
- Registry: registry/repo.yaml
- Routing: knowledge/googleads/TASK_ROUTER.yaml
